title.narrative: Heath Sector Support Programme Technical Assistance (TA)

description.narrative: This activity (Heath Sector Support Programme Technical Assistance (TA)) is a component of Malawi Health Sector Support Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £12,861,231. This component benefits Malawi, and works in the following sector(s): Health policy and administrative management. , with the following implementing partners: AECOM, Charles Kendall Group, Options Consultancy Services, Oxford Policy Management. The start date is 15-11-2010 and the end date is 30-12-2018.
